{"type": "article", "id": 7789, "title": "Primeknit-constructed Stan Smith 灰色款", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-26T07:31:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135201e4PYNU7cv3ra8tws.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAdidas Originals 球鞋系列 Stan Smith 可谓长盛不衰的典范，继去年推出编织款式 Primeknit-constructed Stan Smith，今年春天又在此基础上推出了灰色编织款，织网面上看起来像是布满灰色和黑色的斑点，黑白灰的搭配优雅又不落俗套。这款鞋目前售价 147.63 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.titolo.ch/adidasstansmithprimeknitnm-p-11247.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351583udUVKoTcsiwmWJ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135159eT4BGQMpPJO2haNq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135159DVP2sBTU9fFWzgx8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135200MJUEpQqbftsIAF7P.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height